snippet.title: Gamehelper.com - World in Conflict Yulja Video
snippet.description:
This video is entitled "Yulja" and will give you a flavor of the single player campaign missions from the Soviet perspective (these are the missions that are being added to the great single player campaign that was included in last year's release).  

http://www.gamehelper.com
